OL,3,CWhat are passengers entitled to if
OL,4,Ctheir flight has been affected by fog?
OL,6,FHundreds of passengers have faced
OL,7,Fcancellations or delays after fog
OL,8,Faffected flights at Gatwick Airport
OL,9,Ffor a fourth day.
OL,11,FFlights at the UK's second busiest
OL,12,Fairport have been disrupted since
OL,13,FFriday because of fog.
OL,15,FMany travellers were left needing
OL,16,Fassistance or compensation on Sunday,
OL,17,Fthe airport's busiest day of the
OL,18,Fholiday season.
OL,20,FHere's how to get help if your flight
OL,21,Fis affected by fog.
