OL,3,CWhat are passengers entitled to if
OL,4,Ctheir flight has been affected by fog?
OL,6,F` What flights are covered by UK
OL,7,Fconsumer law?
OL,9,FFlights operated by an airline
OL,10,Fdeparting from a UK airport, flights
OL,11,Foperated by a UK or EU airline
OL,12,Farriving at a UK airport, or flights
OL,13,Foperated by a UK airline arriving at
OL,14,Fan EU airport are covered.
OL,16,F` How long must a flight be delayed
OL,17,Fbefore I am entitled to assistance?
OL,19,FIt depends on the distance of the
OL,20,Fflight.
