OL,3,CWhat are passengers entitled to if
OL,4,Ctheir flight has been affected by fog?
OL,6,FFor flights under 1,500km (932 miles),
OL,7,Fsuch as from Glasgow to Amsterdam, it
OL,8,Fis at least two hours.
OL,10,FFor flights between 1,500km (932
OL,11,Fmiles) and 3,500km (2,175 miles), such
OL,12,Fas from Manchester to Marrakesh, it is
OL,13,Fat least three hours.
OL,15,FFor flights over 3,500km (2,175
OL,16,Fmiles), such as from Heathrow to New
OL,17,FYork, it is at least four hours.
