OL,3,CWhat are passengers entitled to if
OL,4,Ctheir flight has been affected by fog?
OL,6,FA reasonable amount of food and drink
OL,7,F(often via vouchers), a means for you
OL,8,Fto communicate (often by refunding the
OL,9,Fcost of phone calls), and
OL,10,Faccommodation and transfers if an
OL,11,Fovernight stay is required.
OL,13,F` What happens in reality?
OL,15,FAirlines often fail to provide this
OL,16,Fassistance during major disruption due
OL,17,Fto being overwhelmed by requests and
OL,18,Fthere being a shortage of available
OL,19,Frooms in local hotels.
