OL,3,CWhat are passengers entitled to if
OL,4,Ctheir flight has been affected by fog?
OL,6,FThe Civil Aviation Authority (CAA)
OL,7,Fsays in this scenario, passengers can
OL,8,Forganise their own assistance and
OL,9,Fclaim the costs back from the airline
OL,10,Fby submitting receipts.
OL,12,FThe CAA advises passengers not to
OL,13,F"spend more than is reasonable".
OL,15,F` How long must assistance be provided
OL,16,Ffor?
OL,18,FUntil your flight takes off or you
OL,19,Faccept a refund after deciding not to
OL,20,Ftravel.
