OL,3,CWhat are passengers entitled to if
OL,4,Ctheir flight has been affected by fog?
OL,6,F` What about getting to my destination?
OL,8,FIf a flight is cancelled, airlines are
OL,9,Frequired to issue a full refund or get
OL,10,Fyou to your destination if you still
OL,11,Fwant to travel.
OL,13,FMost will book you on to another of
OL,14,Ftheir flights but you may be entitled
OL,15,Fto travel with another airline or by
OL,16,Fan alternative mode of transport if it
OL,17,Fwill get you to your destination
OL,18,Fsignificantly sooner.
