OL,6,F` Am I entitled to compensation for a
OL,7,Fdelayed flight?
OL,9,FAirlines are only liable for
OL,10,Fcompensation if the reason for a delay
OL,11,Fis deemed within their control, such
OL,12,Fas a fault with the aircraft or pilot
OL,13,Fsickness.
